title: Comedor de Zully
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Fast food, Juice bar, Mexican, Oaxacan, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Was all-veg but has added a meat dish per Oct 2013 report. Offer vegetarian versions of traditional homestyle dishes with a different menu each day; plus veggie burgers, tostadas, memelitas, and other fast food. Uses authentic local recipes like fava bean and pea stew, hibiscus flower salad, Oaxacan mole. Pleasant, historical courtyard. Attached to the Pochote Market.
